									</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td valign="top">
									<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
										<tbody>
											<tr>
												<td style="padding: 10px 0px 0px 0px;" width="100%">
												<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
													<tbody>
														<tr>
															<td bgcolor="#ffffff" class="pc-w520-padding-10-30-10-30 pc-w620-padding-10-35-10-35" style="padding: 25px 25px 25px 25px; height: unset; border-radius: 10px 10px 10px 10px; background-color: #ffffff; box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.02);" valign="top">
															<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
																<tbody>
																	<tr>
																		<td align="left" valign="top">
																		<div class="pc-font-alt" style="text-decoration: none;">
																		<div style="font-size:15px;line-height:21px;text-align:left;text-align-last:left;color:#333333;font-family:'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0.2px;">
																		<div style="font-family:'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21px;">Dear {{RecipientName}},</span></div>

																		<div>&nbsp;</div>

																		<div style="font-family:'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif;font-weight:700;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21px;">Welcome to Lydiam Group.</span></div>

																		<div>&nbsp;</div>

																		<div style="font-family:'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21px;">We are delighted to confirm your successful onboarding into our digital asset and foreign exchange services. It is our pleasure to support your trading and treasury requirements through our institutional-grade platform, offering seamless access to global liquidity, competitive pricing, and end-to-end execution support.</span></div>

																		<div>&nbsp;</div>

																		<div style="font-family:'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21px;">Your unique Lydiam Group Reference Number is: </span><span style="font-family: 'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21px;">{{ReferenceNumber}}</span></div>

																		<div style="font-family:'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21px;">(Please reference this number when making payments. Deal tickets will be formatted as: {{ReferenceNumber}}-01, where the suffix corresponds to each specific deal booked.)</span></div>
																		</div>
																		</div>
